{{2001 SEC football standings}}
The '''2001 Mississippi State Bulldogs football team''' represented [[Mississippi State University]] during the [[2001 NCAA Division I-A football season|2001 college football season]]. The team's head coach was [[Jackie Sherrill]]. The Bulldogs played their home games in 2001 at [[Davis Wade Stadium]] in [[Starkville, Mississippi]]

